{"tid":1228194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屌根本成件事好撚諷刺","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:31:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T16:51:31.000Z","uid":38780,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a9625a37de8b8364ef2db1e12bf40f557e2faf4c","tid":1228194,"uid":38780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"開口埋口就話台灣殺人案唔可以就咁不了了之<br />\n唔可以輕視生命乜乜柒柒<br />\n屌你老母12號就射頭打頭打到仆街<br />\n幾撚多人入哂醫院<br />\n今日又一個義士失去左生命<br />\n理性D咁講 <br />\n你要為一條生命硬推條例<br />\n但係就去制造流血/漠視其他既生命<br />\n係咪要死多幾個人你先肯撤回啊 柒婆<br />\n你要幾多條命去換你所謂既一條生命既義意啊?<br />\n你個初心講到幾咁正義凜然<br />\n家陣呢? 屌你老母 不知所謂<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家記住聽日一定要上街 不撒不回 <br />\n<br />\n記住我地係唔會接受其他方案</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"62b1cb136dd427e7a492edbee3e5bbc56232af31","tid":1228194,"uid":23373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲有<br />\n釋放被捕義士<br />\n懲處暴力黑警<br />\n官員問責下台</span></strong>"},{"pid":"56675e4c87a2e11827864e1560b605a23dc67f98","tid":1228194,"uid":38780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:33:59.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家記住聽日一定要出黎話畀所有人知<br />\n呢個政府係幾咁無恥 幾咁冷血<br />\n仲好意思話自己身為一個媽媽<br />\n我屌你老母啊"},{"pid":"8250c4105bce3a3ccad01e2d0de54fd87cb035e0","tid":1228194,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62b1cb136dd427e7a492edbee3e5bbc56232af31","tid":1228194,"uid":23373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:33:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲有<br />\n釋放被捕義士<br />\n懲處暴力黑警<br />\n官員問責下台</span></strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:37:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6adc69bcad4f12e2482a49dbb6a7f8734247afc","tid":1228194,"uid